  <brief_title>Safety and Preliminary Efficacy Study of SA4503 in Subjects Recovering From Ischemic Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Ascending Dose, Phase IIa Study of Safety and Motor Function Restoration in Subjects Treated With SA4503 Following Acute Ischemic Stroke</official_title>
