  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and tolerability of SA4503 in patients
      recovering from a recent stroke. Secondary, to evaluate the efficacy of SA4503 compared to
      placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
